text:
Kushal Punjabi (23 April 1977 – 26 December 2019) was an Indian actor. He won the TV reality game show, ', the Indian version of the American game show "Wipeout" in February 2011.
Punjabi had been in movies such as "Lakshya", "Kaal" and in "Ssshhhh...Phir Koi Hai." He had also appeared in television shows such as "Ishq Mei Marjawan".
Punjabi hung himself at his Mumbai home on 26 December 2019 at the age of 42.
